      "id": "1717049962186",
      "question_pmp": "A newly assigned project manager for an infrastructure upgrade project is reviewing the project charter. The charter vaguely mentions the need for 'sufficient technical staff' to execute the project, without specifying roles or numbers. During the Initiating phase, what action should the project manager prioritize to begin addressing this resource requirement?",
